imageDescription: An image of a broken mirror, shattered into pieces, represents the song "Nervous Breakdown." The fragmented reflection symbolizes the disarray and inner turmoil described in the lyrics, highlighting the feeling of being mentally and emotionally shattered. The sharp edges and jagged lines convey the intense emotions and the desire to escape the pain.
